The '''Copa del Rey 1936''' is the 34th staging of the [[Copa del Rey]].

The competition started between January to April, 1936 and concluded on June 21, 1936 with the Final, held at the [[Estadio Mestalla|Mestalla]] stadium in [[Valencia, Spain|Valencia]].

